{
  "act_id": "act_horizontal",
  "title": "Horizontal Motion Story",
  "viz_panel": "svg",
  "beats": [
    {
      "say": "Let's zoom in on the horizontal motion. Notice something crucial — once the arrow leaves the bow, no forces push or pull it sideways.",
      "card": {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Key insight: Air resistance ignored, gravity acts only downward. No horizontal forces during flight."
      },
      "viz_actions": [
        {
          "method": "isolateMotion",
          "params": {
            "motionType": "horizontal",
            "dimOpacity": 0.3
          },
          "offset": 0
        },
        {
          "method": "highlightComponent",
          "params": {
            "component": "horizontal",
            "intensity": 1.2
          },
          "offset": "+0.8"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "say": "This means the horizontal velocity stays rock-steady at 34.6 meters per second. Not speeding up, not slowing down — constant throughout the entire flight.",
      "card": {
        "type": "latex",
        "content": "v_x = 34.6 \\text{ m/s} = \\text{constant}",
        "highlight": true
      },
      "viz_actions": [
        {
          "method": "updateVelocityComponents",
          "params": {
            "time": 2.0,
            "showVectors": true
          },
          "offset": 0
        },
        {
          "method": "createMotionGraph",
          "params": {
            "type": "velocity",
            "axis": "horizontal",
            "realTime": false
          },
          "offset": "+1.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "say": "For horizontal position, it's simple multiplication. Distance equals velocity times time: x equals 34.6t. Watch how the arrow moves sideways at this steady pace.",
      "card": {
        "type": "latex",
        "content": "x(t) = v_x \\cdot t = 34.6t \\text{ meters}",
        "highlight": true
      },
      "viz_actions": [
        {
          "method": "showEquation",
          "params": {
            "equation": "x = 34.6t",
            "position": "top-right",
            "style": "highlight"
          },
          "offset": 0
        },
        {
          "method": "pulseObject",
          "params": {
            "objectId": "arrow",
            "intensity": 1.1,
            "duration": 0.6
          },
          "offset": "+1.2"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}